room_title: Escape room "The Magician’s Audition" by Escape Rooms Unlocked in Fort Myers
room_address: 401 E Olympia Ave, Punta Gorda, FL 33950
room_description: Max the Magnificent is the greatest magician in the world, and he just announced that he’s looking for an apprentice! This is your chance to fulfill your lifelong dream of becoming an illusionist. However, Max demands his student be nothing but the best. The magician has set up a mystifying set of puzzles, riddles, and, naturally, magic tricks. In order to become his apprentice, you need to prove your skills by completing Max’s challenge and escaping the puzzle in 60 minutes!
